  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain the <strong>tofu</strong> and crumble it with your fingers directly into the pan</p><p>Add the <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and the <strong>small soy sauce<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(save the larger one<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span>for later) to the tofu and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to crisp – this is your crispy <strong>scrambled tofu</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1615910155443-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1615910155443-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1615910155443-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1615910155443-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1615910155443-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is crisp, add it to a plate and set aside</p><p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong> to the pan with the<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1615910177600-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1615910177600-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1615910177600-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1615910177600-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1615910177600-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>rainbow veg mix </strong>and cook for 2-3 min further until the veg has started to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1615910197419-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1615910197419-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1615910197419-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1615910197419-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1615910197419-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has softened slightly, add the <strong>udon noodles</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong>, <strong>mirin </strong>and the <strong>large soy sauce<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until all the noodles are coated and cook for 1 min further until warmed through – these are your <strong>yaki udon noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
